OL,3,CCEO who snatched tennis player's hat
OL,4,Cfrom young boy says he made 'huge
OL,5,Cmistake'
OL,7,FA Polish millionaire who went viral
OL,8,Fafter he was filmed taking a player's
OL,9,Fhat intended for a young boy at the US
OL,10,FOpen has issued an apology.
OL,12,FThe clip saw Polish tennis player
OL,13,FKamil Majchrzak offering his hat to an
OL,14,Feagerly awaiting boy before Piotr
OL,15,FSzczerek took it out of Majchrzak's
OL,16,Fhand.
OL,18,FMajchrzak, who was signing autographs
OL,19,Fat the time, did not notice the
OL,20,Fexchange, but the boy was visibly
OL,21,Fupset that he did not get the hat.
