OL,7,FThe clip quickly went viral with
OL,8,Fpeople criticising Szczerek, the CEO
OL,9,Fof Polish paving company Drogbruk, for
OL,10,Fhis behaviour towards the child.
OL,12,FOn his company's Instagram account,
OL,13,FSzczerek said in Polish he had made a
OL,14,F"huge mistake."
OL,16,FHe said: "Due to the situation that
OL,17,Fhappened during Kamil Majchrzak's
OL,18,Fmatch at the US Open, I would like to
OL,19,Funequivocally apologise to the injured
OL,20,Fboy, his family, all the fans, and the
OL,21,Fplayer himself."
OL,1,W~s1{$~k4{$k7                    G2/7
