OL,7,FHe added: "In the midst of emotion,
OL,8,Famidst the crowd's celebration after
OL,9,Fthe victory, I was convinced that the
OL,10,Ftennis player was passing the cap to
OL,11,Fme ` for my sons, who had previously
OL,12,Fasked for autographs. This mistaken
OL,13,Fbelief caused me to instinctively
OL,14,Freach out.
OL,16,F"Today, I know that I did something
OL,17,Fthat looked like I deliberately took a
OL,18,Fsouvenir from a child.
OL,1,W~s1{$~k4{$k7                    G3/7
