OL,7,F"It wasn't my intention, but that
OL,8,Fdoesn't change the fact that I hurt
OL,9,Fthe boy and disappointed the fans."
OL,11,FIn the post, he confirmed he had given
OL,12,Fthe hat back to the boy.
OL,14,FHe also made clear this was his only
OL,15,Fcomment on the incident, and that
OL,16,Fneither he nor his family had said
OL,17,Fanything else on social media. Any
OL,18,Fother statement made online was fake,
OL,19,Fhe said.
