OL,12,FSzczerek added: "For years, my wife
OL,13,Fand I have been involved in helping
OL,14,Fchildren and young athletes, but this
OL,15,Fsituation has shown me that one moment
OL,16,Fof disregard can undo years of work
OL,17,Fand support. This is a painful but
OL,18,Fnecessary lesson in humility for me.
