OL,7,F"Therefore, I will be even more
OL,8,Factively involved in initiatives
OL,9,Fsupporting children and young people
OL,10,Fand in actions against violence and
OL,11,Fhate. I believe that only through
OL,12,Factions can I rebuild lost trust."
OL,14,FAfter Majchrzak saw the clip, he
OL,15,Fposted on Instagram asking people to
OL,16,Fhelp him get in touch with the young
OL,17,Fboy. He later shared an image with the
OL,18,Fchild, who he identified as Brock,
OL,19,Fwearing the cap.
